{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "第八回\"圆月山庄\"：柳若松携蓝蓝赴圆月山庄丁鹏之宴。凌虚发现柳若松带来的并非其妻子而是一名陌生女子，怒斥其有辱武当门风。柳若松公然宣布叛出武当，与凌虚拔剑相向，以\"天外流星\"一招刺死凌虚。丁鹏现身与柳若松对峙，约定以庄院和万松山庄为赌注决斗。丁鹏以弯刀一刀击败柳若松，在其脸上划出血十字。蓝蓝随即露出真面目——她是满翠院妓女翠仙，被丁鹏花六万两银子赎出冒充蓝蓝。原来\"蓝蓝\"就是青青乔装，整件事是丁鹏精心设计的报复计划，让柳若松身败名裂。柳若松走投无路，竟跪求丁鹏收他为徒。章末丁鹏回到小楼与青青相聚，讲述了柳若松的下场。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你好！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你好！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你一定已经等了我很久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "现在我们是不是可以走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你说什么时候走，我们就什么时候走。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你知道柳若松是贫道的同门？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你们是老朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "叫她回去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "叫谁回去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这个女人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "你不知道她是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "不管她是谁，都叫她回去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "这里的确有个人应该回去，但却绝不是她。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "不是她是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "是你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "你若跪下来跟她磕三个头，赶快滚回去，我也许就会饶了你。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "我已经说得很清楚，你也应该听得很清楚。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你忘了本门的戒律第一条是什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "本门是哪一门？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你难道连你自己是哪一门的弟子都忘了？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "以前我的确在武当门下呆过，可是现在却已跟武当全无半点关系。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你已不是武当门下？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "是谁将你逐出了武当？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "是我自己要走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你自己要叛师出门？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "我要来就来，要走就走，也谈不上什么叛师出门。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "好，很好，好极了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "你还有没有别的话说？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_xu",
      "speaker_name": "凌虚",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "没有了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ling_xu",
      "text": "那么你为何还不拔剑？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我很好，可是你一定不太好。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我在你新的庄院里，杀了你请来的客人，你怎么会好？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我看你非但心情不好，运气也不会好。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为你又遇到了我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "不错，每次遇见你，好像我都要倒霉的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你说得不错，每次你只要看见我，就会倒霉的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这次呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这次恐怕不太一样了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "因为这次是在你的地方，你有帮手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这是我们两个之间的事，我绝不会让第三个人出手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "那就好极了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你杀了凌虚道长，自然有武当门下去找你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我若杀了你呢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "只要你能胜我一招，不但随时可以割下我的头颅来，这片庄院也是你的，死人已用不着这么大的地方。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "正确。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "无论谁死了，只要有七尺黄土就已足够，所以……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "所以我若败了，我也会将我那万松山庄送给你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这才是公平的交易。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我们一言为定。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "有天下英雄在这里作证，就算想赖，也赖不了的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "看你的剑！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我已发誓，今生不再用剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你用什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "用刀。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你若用刀，我可以让你三招。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "看你的刀！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这就是我的刀。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我看得见。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "这柄刀还没有饮过人血，因为今日还是我第一次试刀。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "你用我来试刀？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "就因为我要用你来试刀，所以我还可以让你占个便宜。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "只要你能接得住我三刀，就算你胜了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "好，我就看你这三刀。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你看不见的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我知道你看不见的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你至少要再练十年，才能看得见我三刀。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "现在我一刀就已足够。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你败了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我败了。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "看起来好像是你败了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你说过，我不会败的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我说过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你说过，只要有你在，我就绝不会败。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你一定是听错了，我怎么会说这种话？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我没有听错，你说过你会帮我的，你为什么不出手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我怎么出手，我能帮你做什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "远处的人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她惟一能帮你做的事，就是帮你把裤子脱下来。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点都不错，我惟一能帮你做的好像只有这件事，这种事我最内行。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "speaker_name": "柳若松",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你……你究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蓝",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你花了六万两银子，把我从'满翠院'赎出来，叫我在会仙楼等你，陪你到这里来作客，而且还用那么大一顶轿子去接我！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_xian",
      "speaker_name": "翠仙",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "你怎么会连我是谁都不知道？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_xian",
      "speaker_name": "翠仙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是翠仙，这里至少有一百个人认得我！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_liu_ruo_song",
      "text": "我是蓝蓝，我就是惟一可以救你的人，只有我能对抗青青。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你为什么不点灯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "现在大家都已经开始在喝酒了，所以我就抽空找了个机会，溜回来看看你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我一定要回来告诉你，我们的计划已经成功了，我已经彻底毁了柳若松。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "如果你也能看见柳若松发现他心目中救苦救难的仙子竟是个妓女时，脸上那种表情，你一定也会觉得开心的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "如果你是他，到了那种时候，你会怎么样？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你猜猜看！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你猜他做出件什么样的事？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他逃走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "他自己也知道逃不了的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "就算能逃得了，也无路可走，无处可去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他晕了过去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "凌虚的朋友杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他杀死了那个女人，然后再横剑自尽？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "他没有死，他还舍不得死。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "他做出的那件事，无论谁都想不到这世上真的有人能做得出来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_ding_peng",
      "text": "他怎么样了？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_peng",
      "speaker_name": "丁鹏",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "别人都以为他会来找我拼命的时候，他却忽然跪下来求我，一定要我收他做徒弟。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 824,
      "line_end": 826
    }
  ],
